Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.71,0:19:21.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骗人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.21,0:19:25.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天是我的..忌日..
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.25,0:19:43.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你..你要干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.60,0:19:50.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住..住手！
